---
/*
max-w-md px-4 sm:max-w-2xl

sm:px-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-4xl

lg:px-0 xl:max-w-5xl 2xl:max-w-6xl
*/
---

<div>
  <section
    class="flex items-center justify-center flex-col py-36 md:py-48 max-w-md px-6 sm:max-w-2xl sm:px-8 md:max-w-3xl md:px-10 lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-4 xl:max-w-5xl 2xl:max-w-6xl mx-auto"
  >
    <h1
      class="text-4xl font-bold text-center tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-[4rem] xl:text-[6rem] 2xl:text-[6.5rem]"
    >
      Markdown sharing, <br /><span class="text-violet-400">fast</span> and <span
        class="text-blue-500">easy</span
      >
    </h1>
  </section>
</div>
